data.description: Beautiful and immaculate single-story gem in the desirable Siena community of Round Rock, TX! Nestled within steps of community amenities & backing to a serene park, this meticulously-maintained & lightly-lived in residence offers both exclusivity & comfort. The stunning stone & stucco front façade coupled with lush landscaping beckon you to experience the finest in suburban living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an abundance of natural light that fills the luxurious interior. High ceilings & beautiful hardwood flooring extend throughout the main living areas, creating an open & inviting atmosphere. Prepare to be wowed by the gourmet kitchen, where culinary dreams come to life. Showcasing a center island, breakfast bar, granite countertops, & chic white shaker cabinetry, the kitchen is a true masterpiece. The suite of sleek stainless-steel appliances, including a refrigerator, elevates both form & function. The living room provides the perfect space for relaxation or entertaining, with its warm ambiance & easy flow to the covered back patio. Step outside & envision hosting gatherings, firing up the grill, or simply enjoying a quiet moment with a cup of coffee. The primary bedroom, thoughtfully separated from the secondary bedrooms, offers a large walk-in closet & private en-suite bath complete with a granite-topped double vanity & an oversized walk-in shower. The secondary bedrooms are generously sized & share a well-appointed guest bathroom, ensuring comfort for family & guests alike. The backyard beckons with ample space for activities, while the covered patio presents an ideal setting for outdoor enjoyment, be it a barbecue or a serene afternoon lounging. The Siena community is renowned for its exceptional amenities, including a sparkling pool, park, playground, sand volleyball court, & basketball court. Convenience is key, as this home boasts easy access to freeways, shops, restaurants, & the beloved Old Settler's Park. Schedule a showing today!
